## Deliberate divergences from upstream

This skill keeps `.drawio` as the source of truth and does NOT delete the
intermediate `.drawio` file after a PNG / SVG / PDF export, diverging from
the upstream skill-cli step 4 ("then delete the source `.drawio` file").
Retaining the source keeps the diagram round-trippable without decoding
embedded XML from the exported image.
